cessible. This initiative follows his popularity on social media. The first stream is scheduled for May 21. The show will also be available on other platforms.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/zohran-mamdani-enters-streamer-era-with-live-twitch-series-talk-with-the-people/articleshow/131251342.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/zohran-mamdani-enters-streamer-era-with-live-twitch-series-talk-with-the-people/articleshow/131251342.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-22T00:48:33+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Sumit Roy</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131251323,imgsize-586694.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Air France and Airbus held guilty over deadly 2009 Atlantic flight disaster]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131250427.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Air France and Airbus have been found guilty of manslaughter by a Paris appeals court for the 2009 crash of Flight 447, which killed all 228 people on board. The court overturned a previous ruling, holding both companies responsible for the tragedy. Fined €225,000 each, the companies plan to appeal the verdict, while victims' families seek greater accountability.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/air-france-and-airbus-held-guilty-over-deadly-2009-atlantic-flight-disaster/articleshow/131250427.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/uk/air-france-and-airbus-held-guilty-over-deadly-2009-atlantic-flight-disaster/articleshow/131250427.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-05-21T23:45:22+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131250436,imgsize-3